Package: RscheduleR
Type: Package
Title: Interface to scheduleR for scheduling R scripts, Markdown reports and
    Shiny apps.
Description: Interface to scheduleR for scheduling R scripts, Markdown reports
    and Shiny apps. Sets up the default user, and creates an RStudio addin.
